---
import { PERSONAL_INFO } from "../../data/personal";
import Section from "../UI/Section.astro";
import Title from "../UI/Title.astro";
import Badge from "../UI/Badge.astro";
---

<Section id="about" title="About Us" class="mt-0 mb-0 py-0">
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-1 mx-auto" data-aos="fade-left">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-light">
            We’re Josh and Ben — friendly, experienced online tutors helping students feel confident and exam-ready in Science, Maths, and Physics.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-light">
            <span class="text-white font-semibold">Josh</span> specialises in GCSE & A-Level Biology and Chemistry, teaching online nationwide (Birmingham-based) with 8+ years’ experience. He supports AQA, OCR, Edexcel, and IB, with a clear focus on exam technique and past paper mastery.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-light">
            <span class="text-white font-semibold">Ben</span> specialises in GCSE, A-Level & IB Physics and Maths, teaching online only. With strong AQA, OCR, Edexcel, and IB knowledge, he helps students build results through smart problem-solving, clear feedback, and examiner-style thinking.
        </p>
    </div>
</Section>
